      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SKEDADDLE PERCY (8) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (22.29), beaten 2.25 lengths. Finished second the start before. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Tough to beat if on-song. RIVIA THEA (3) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at this track in a Grade 4/5 (22.26). Will strip fitter for the run. Expected to feature again. INTRODUCED (2) ran a good time (21.81) winning a Grade 5 two back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing fourth at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. FEAT OF STRENGTH (7) drops in trip and should be in the mix.",
